Class ImplShrController<T extends ShrEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sprhibrad.framework.controller.ShrController<T>

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UserPrefsController

    public abstract class ImplShrController<T extends ShrEntity>
extends ShrController<T>
    This class is the driver for overriding during the writing of a SprHibRAD based application controller class. It provides the main signatures that the ide shows the developer. It can be see as an invocation adapter of the ShrController methods.
